    <item>
      <title>Smoke engulfs buildings after Israeli forces strike Beirut suburbs – video</title>
      <link>https://www.theguardian.com/world/video/2026/mar/06/smoke-engulfs-buildings-israeli-forces-strike-beirut-suburbs-lebanon-video</link>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Footage showed the aftermath of an Israeli strike in the south of Lebanon's capital, a day after Israel issued a mass evacuation order for the south of the country. The Israeli military carried out further strikes on Beirut’s southern Dahiyeh suburb, as well as towns in southern Lebanon. The Lebanese health ministry said 217 people had been killed in Israeli attacks since Monday, according to the Reuters news agency&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.theguardian.com/world/2026/mar/06/us-israel-threaten-major-escalation-airstrikes-iran-lebanon"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;US and Israel threaten major escalation as airstrikes bombard Iran and Lebanon&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.theguardian.com/world/live/2026/mar/06/iran-war-live-updates-us-temporarily-lets-india-buy-russian-oil-amid-energy-fears-israeli-military-launches-strikes-on-beirut"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Middle East crisis – live updates&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.theguardian.com/world/video/2026/mar/06/smoke-engulfs-buildings-israeli-forces-strike-beirut-suburbs-lebanon-video"&gt;Continue reading...&lt;/a&gt;</description>
      <category domain="https://www.theguardian.com/world/lebanon">Lebanon</category>
