    <item>
      <title>Nigel Farage to discuss Chagos Islands deal at Mar-a-Lago dinner with Donald Trump tonight – as it happened</title>
      <link>https://www.theguardian.com/politics/live/2026/mar/06/david-lammy-raf-jets-cyprus-iran-middle-east-labour-keir-starmer-uk-politics-live-news-updates</link>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Reform UK leader told a ‘Save Chagos Boat Party’ yesterday he would be raising the issue in his meeting with the president&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A second government charter flight to bring UK nationals back from the Middle East is due to depart Oman this evening, Downing Street has confirmed.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Further flights are expected in the coming days and more than 160,000 British nationals have now registered their presence with the Foreign Office in the region.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The deputy prime minister is sliding down the slippery slope to full conflict by backing direct UK strikes on military positions in Iran.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;We need an urgent clarification from number 10 on whether this is a change in Britain’s position on involvement in Trump’s illegal war.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;We must not copy Trump’s unconstitutional and illegal approach to war in the Middle East.&lt;/p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.theguardian.com/politics/live/2026/mar/06/david-lammy-raf-jets-cyprus-iran-middle-east-labour-keir-starmer-uk-politics-live-news-updates"&gt;Continue reading...&lt;/a&gt;</description>
      <category domain="https://www.theguardian.com/politics/politics">Politics</category>
      <category domain="https://www.theguardian.com/politics/nigel-farage">Nigel Farage</category>
      <category domain="https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/donaldtrump">Donald Trump</category>
      <category domain="https://www.theguardian.com/world/chagos-islands">Chagos Islands</category>
      <category domain="https://www.theguardian.com/world/us-israel-war-on-iran">US-Israel war on Iran</category>
      <category domain="https://www.theguardian.com/politics/keir-starmer">Keir Starmer</category>
      <category domain="https://www.theguardian.com/world/iran">Iran</category>
      <category domain="https://www.theguardian.com/politics/david-lammy">David Lammy</category>
      <category domain="https://www.theguardian.com/uk/uk">UK news</category>
      <category domain="https://www.theguardian.com/world/cyprus">Cyprus</category>
      <category domain="https://www.theguardian.com/world/middleeast">Middle East and north Africa</category>
      <pubDate>Fri, 06 Mar 2026 16:02:30 GMT</pubDate>
      <guid>https://www.theguardian.com/politics/live/2026/mar/06/david-lammy-raf-jets-cyprus-iran-middle-east-labour-keir-starmer-uk-politics-live-news-updates</guid>
      <media:content width="140" url="https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/fcf63f02256e9b713c3f1c7b11ce845c5ad555a8/1875_1213_3349_2678/master/3349.jpg?width=140&amp;quality=85&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=max&amp;s=198e373a2b028fc96b54ed80958f38a3">
        <media:credit scheme="urn:ebu">Photograph: Neil Hall/EPA</media:credit>
      </media:content>
      <media:content width="460" url="https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/fcf63f02256e9b713c3f1c7b11ce845c5ad555a8/1875_1213_3349_2678/master/3349.jpg?width=460&amp;quality=85&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=max&amp;s=e07fa1371c79e1d4a4efeaeb7a1abee5">
        <media:credit scheme="urn:ebu">Photograph: Neil Hall/EPA</media:credit>
      </media:content>
      <media:content width="700" url="https://i.guim.co.uk/img/media/fcf63f02256e9b713c3f1c7b11ce845c5ad555a8/1875_1213_3349_2678/master/3349.jpg?width=700&amp;quality=85&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=max&amp;s=72be92ce0d34d78b531720174b33aaab">
        <media:credit scheme="urn:ebu">Photograph: Neil Hall/EPA</media:credit>
